{"tid":635493,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭松泰被保皇狗動議dq","createTime":"2018-04-20T07:21:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-19T04:40:02.000Z","uid":38523,"like":18,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1b79ba623ebfe9a0928c002fde411bb9672d3d6c","tid":635493,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T07:21:53.000Z","msg":"大家睇下自稱白票本土派<br />\n又話自己唔係放生保皇狗<br />\n否認係保皇狗打手既關愛座hunter<br />\n點回應？<br />\n當然唔係屌柒始作俑者保皇狗啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/14/172458_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F14%2F172458_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=1fbf46d4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家自己睇算如果咁都唔係叫幫保皇狗轉移視線<br />\n點先叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw<br />\n得等睇佢又入來話我係泛民打手<br />\n但其實大家都心知<br />\n我係又好唔係又好<br />\n點唔係解釋來<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18596e44a9b5c8f5979b0d224a137851f87efa64","tid":635493,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T07:26:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59e45f719d311dfbc8e8d9cee3154e0e34d9e30a","tid":635493,"uid":47359,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T07:31:30.000Z","msg":"次次一屌泛民賣港<br />\n泛民狙擊手就會屈我係五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又屈本土派user係我分身<br />\n<br />\n五毛狙擊手屈完本土派user係我分身未?<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/634064/1?ref=android\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/634064/1?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\nLIHKG @ Android<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/20/153052_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src